#

Teriyaki Chicken Rice Bowl

25 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Fat

Cuisine:

JapaneseAmerican

Course:

Main DishDinner

Tags:

Quick MealComfort FoodAsian Cuisine

Description

A flavorful and satisfying rice bowl featuring tender chicken glazed in a sweet and savory teriyaki sauce, served over fluffy rice and topped with fresh vegetables.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 lb
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/2 cup
  • cooked rice: 2 cups
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • carrot: 1, sliced
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
